Looking for a Ford F150 near Washington?

The Ford F150 has to be many things to many people. From work truck to cruiser, off-road vehicle to boat hauler, there is an F-150 for virtually every task. As a result, the lineup is diverse. There are four engines available on the F-150, six trims and several body options. With the largest selection of cars from dealers and private sellers, Autotrader can help find the perfect F150 for you.

Autotrader has 2,273 Ford F150s for sale near Washington, DC, including a Used 2006 Ford F150 2WD SuperCab, a Used 2006 Ford F150 4x4 SuperCab, and a Used 2006 Ford F150 4x4 SuperCrew XLT.

Not sure if a F150 is the right fit for you?
